	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
其实吧，<delay8 />我考虑了很久，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最后决定要搬出这座岛。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当然了，<tag a="110" b="33" />的<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生活环境很好，<delay8 />是一座非常棒的<tag a="110" b="32" />！<delay40 />不过<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还是想看看外面的世界！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">留在这里吧！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">这样啊……</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂、<delay8 />喂！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实，<delay20 />再过不久，
我就要搬出这座<tag a="110" b="32" />了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然这里的生活环境<delay8 />很舒适，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但去到外面，为了寻求新的邂逅而冒险，<delay20 />
感觉也很不错，不是吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我不要你离开！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">保重……</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实吧，<delay20 />
我有一件事<delay8 />要告诉你。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上已经留下了很多美好的回忆。<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我在考虑，<delay20 />
要不要搬去一个新的环境居住！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不要走！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">是这样啊</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶？<delay20 />你这是要挽留我吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呜呜<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />你都这么说了，<delay20 />
就算是我<delay8 />也不忍心走了啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay8 />我还是放弃搬家的打算，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />继续留在<delay8 />这座岛上生活吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后也请继续多多关照了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶？<delay20 />既然你都这么说了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我又怎么忍心离开这里<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，我还是暂时放弃搬家的念头吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算要搬出这座<tag a="110" b="32" />，<delay20 />也要等我们
<delay8 />好好畅谈一番之后再说。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇！<delay20 />没想到你会这样说呢！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你还真是个重情义的人啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你，<delay8 />能来挽留我。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你都这样说了，<delay20 />
我还怎么忍心<delay8 />搬走。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />搬家的事<delay8 />缓一缓再说吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你<delay8 />一直以来对我的照顾。<delay40 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就知道，<delay20 />像你这么温柔的人，<delay8 />
不会强硬地要我留下的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后不管去到哪里，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生活在这座岛上的美好回忆，<delay8 />
都会是我<delay8 />一生的珍宝。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很高兴<delay8 />能和你成为好朋友。<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我离开的那天，<delay8 />你记得要笑着来送我哦！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不然<delay8 />我会舍不得的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我还要准备打包搬家的行李，<delay8 />
可能会比较忙，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但你有空<delay8 />也可以来找我聊聊哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在<tag a="110" b="33" />的生活<delay8 />
真的非常开心！<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很庆幸当时选择了来到这里生活。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特别是<delay20 />我还在这里与你相遇，<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很感谢你<delay8 />对我那么好。<delay20 />
今后也希望你能每天活力四射哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
